msgstr "Inforuutujen asettelu"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/LayoutConfigPanel.cpp:194
msgid ""
"A list of possible InfoBox layouts. Do some trials to find the best for your "
"screen size."
msgstr ""
"Mahdolliset InfoBox-asettelut. Tee joitain kokeiluja löytääksesi parhaan "
"asetuksen ruudulle."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/LayoutConfigPanel.cpp:197
