#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Eleohjaus\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar tukee kosketuseleitä kartalla:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Pyyhkäisy ylös** (U): Lähennä\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Pyyhkäisy alas** (D): Loitonna\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Pyyhkäisy oikealle** (R): Edellinen "
"näyttötila\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Pyyhkäisy vasemmalle** (L): Seuraava "
"näyttötila\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Ylös-ala** (UD): Automaattinen zoomaus\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Ala-ylös** (DU): Valikko\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Ala-oikea** (DR): Reittipisteen tiedot\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Ala-vasen** (DL): Vaihtoehdot\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Oikea-ala** (RD): Tehtävänhallinta\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Ylös-oikea-ala** (URD): Analyysi\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Vasen-ala-oikea** (LDR): "
"Tarkistuslista\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Ylös-oikea-ala-vasen** (URDL): "
"Panorointitila\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Vasen-ala-oikea-ala-vasen** "
"(LDRDL): Tila\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Ylös-vasen-ala-oikea** (ULDR): "
"Pikavalikko\n"
"\n"
"Siirry panorointitilaan painamalla karttaa pitkään. Panorointitilassa "
"napautus näyttää lähellä olevat reittipisteet."

